                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-[#F4F7F6] border-l-4 border-[#FF8057] p-5 rounded-lg mt-6">
                        <p class="text-gray-800 font-medium">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb text-[#FF8057] mr-2"></i>
                            <strong>Florida Tip:</strong> Pay special attention to areas where grease and humidity combine, like behind the stove and around the sink. Use dehumidification techniques to prevent mold in cabinets. For <a href="/ocala" class="text-[#FF8057] font-semibold hover:underline">Ocala area homes</a>, this extra attention is crucial for maintaining a healthy kitchen environment.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Bathrooms -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-lg border border-[#E3EAE8]/60 mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#FF8057] mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-bath"></i> Bathroom Deep Clean
                    </h3>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-6">
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#305048] mb-4">Deep Cleaning Tasks</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Scrub tile and grout with mold prevention</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Deep clean shower doors and tracks</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Disinfect and descale all fixtures</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Replace caulking if mold is present</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Clean exhaust fan and replace filter</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Sanitize toilet inside and out, including behind</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#305048] mb-4">Organization & Maintenance</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Declutter medicine cabinet and vanity</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Check and replace expired medications</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Deep clean mirrors and light fixtures</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Wash and replace bath mats and curtains</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Organize linen closet and towels</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Test and improve ventilation systems</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-[#F4F7F6] border-l-4 border-[#FF8057] p-5 rounded-lg mt-6">
                        <p class="text-gray-800 font-medium">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-exclamation-triangle text-[#FF8057] mr-2"></i>
                            <strong>Humidity Alert:</strong> Florida bathrooms are mold magnets. Focus on improving ventilation and using mold-resistant products. Consider running exhaust fans for 30+ minutes after showers.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Living Areas -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-lg border border-[#E3EAE8]/60 mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#FF8057] mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-couch"></i> Living Areas & Bedrooms
                    </h3>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#305048] mb-4">Furniture & Fabrics</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Deep clean upholstered furniture</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Vacuum and flip mattresses</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Wash all bedding, pillows, and comforters</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Steam clean carpets and rugs</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Dust and condition wood furniture</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Clean and organize closets completely</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#305048] mb-4">Air Quality & Details</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Replace HVAC filters throughout home</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#305048] mt-1"></i>
                                    <span>Clean air vents and return ducts</span>
